# Dwarf C# disk overlay files written by the emulator on shutdown
# (Phase H .cscheck format). Current + timestamped rotation archives.
# Base disks (.dsk / .zdisk) stay tracked.
*.cscheck
*.cscheck-*
*.cscheck.tmp
